          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "23": {
              "id": "23",
              "speaker": "",
              "text": "Bad news - so many things will be on fire when you step outside of this room. YOU INCLUDED. That's okay, though, right? It's Hell! You expected it to be hot.",
